    <main>
        <section class="return-section">
            <h2>Return & Exchange Policy</h2>

            <h3>Returns</h3>
            <p>If you are not completely satisfied with your purchase, we offer a 30-day return policy. To be eligible for a return, the item must be unused, unworn, and in the same condition that you received it. It must also be in the original packaging.</p>

            <h3>How to Return an Item</h3>
            <p>To initiate a return, please contact our customer service team at support@tshirtstore.com within 30 days of receiving your order. Once we approve your return, we will provide you with return instructions and a return address.</p>

            <h3>Refunds</h3>
            <p>Once your return is received and inspected, we will send you an email notification regarding the approval or rejection of your refund. If approved, your refund will be processed and credited to your original method of payment within 7-10 business days.</p>

            <h3>Exchanges</h3>
            <p>If you would like to exchange an item, please contact us with the details of the item you wish to exchange. We will send you instructions on how to proceed with the exchange.</p>

            <h3>Non-returnable Items</h3>
            <p>Some items are non-returnable, such as sale items, personalized/customized products, and gift cards. Please ensure that the items are eligible for return before sending them back.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

